---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<footer class="bg-base-300 text-base-content pt-16 pb-8 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
      <!-- Brand Section -->
      <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-1">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 group">
          <img
            src="https://i.ibb.co/s9RbYYcv/logo.png"
            onerror="this.src='../src/assets/logo.png'; this.onerror=null;"
            alt="ESIGNA Streetwear Logo"
            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform shadow-lg"
          />
          <!-- <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform shadow-lg"
                    >
                        <Icon
                            name="lucide:shopping-bag"
                            class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-content"
                        />
                    </div> -->
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter gradient-text">
            ESIGNA Streetwear
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Moda y estilo para quienes quieren destacar cada día. Descubre nuestra
          colección de ropa diseñada para combinar comodidad, tendencia y
          personalidad.
        </p>
